replies.body:
{{item:3165}} 
100 AP, 400 Mana, 20% CDR, Mana Restore, Grievous Wounds.

I will argue that Morello's is too important for mages and that it's "not tons of damage" actually kinda is. Cooldowns and  mana restore allow faster cycling which is more needed lately due to how health counters mages more than MR does. (20 AP amp tome needs to hit multiple times to kill 150 HP ruby crystal in raw numbers. This causes mages to need a second cycling of spells to kill a target. This forces a lot of reliance on that "unwanted" CDR.)
